reviews.review_text: Thanks to Megan, an a employee there. I was struggling at the kiosk with my account code and she help me through it. She said she worked there and was getting off her shift. She was so nice to me and wanted to help me. I am very grateful that she help me out. I want to give her great review on how she help a customer who was struggling. Thank you again Megan.
One can expect a good customer service experience. Staff working here are so polite and addresses customers timely even during busy hours.

This Mcdonalds is my go to. Whenever i go there, its very clean. The staff is very friendly. One Indian girl Sukhraj  took my order, she was very polite and even offered my kids balloons and coloring sheets. Thank you soo much for going above and beyond for excellent service.

Walmart mcdonalds is one of the best restaurant. Even if there is staff shortage they always try their 100% to serve customers as quickly as possible with accuracy. Their staff is very polite. I saw if someone has issue with their mobile order or they don t know how to order through their phone, their staff always try to help customers and solve their issue. Indian staff is also very nice. They work very hard to make customers happy with serving accurate and fresh food. So nothing bad about this restaurant. Excellent service.

Next to the McDonalds in Quesnel this is the only other location that still makes good food. This is the first time in years Ive got a fresh made and hot McDonalds meal on the coast. Also sending props to the guy working right now for banging out multiple breakfasts without breaking a sweat. Hes so polite and is doing a great job!

Food is good and the Service so fast and affordable we always buy at McDonalds after my graveyard shift and we buy breakfast because no time for me to cook. Kid-friendliness: Yes they allowed children at the store to eat and have fun and they toys for kids when u buy kids Meal.
Its  a nice little  Macdonald  location.

I visited this mcdonalds just last sunday. Although it s small but it was very clean. The staff is very friendly. One girl  Simran  helped me with the mobile ordering. She was very patient  because my internet was very slow and it was taking longer for processing. I was happy with the service.

Walmart Mcdonalds is one of my favourite restaurant. I have really good experience with this McDonald. This is one of the cleanest McDonald in Richmond. Moreover, I like the Quick and friendly service. I would recommend to customers come here and try the fresh food. Excellent service!.

After a long day of shopping this is a great place to unwind and have a quick bite. The customer service is great the staff are friendly and nice and the food are always hot. What best is they have free WIFI!! Definitely gonna recommend.
